description:
Minecraft Map Making. Today we start with a quick explanation of what Battle Bane is, with a few refinements to the game rules. Then we check out how the game has been modified to work with structure blocks and the new command blocks.

Let's make a map! The goal of this series is to build a PvP arena of sorts, that is capable of a few specific technical functions needed for my game. The most important aspect of this game/map is the game design and rules, not really the map itself. More details will be revealed as we get further into things.
